    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776680/extras/banner_block_em.gif?t=1704818446\" /></span><br><br><i>《Block'Em!》</i>是一款精彩刺激的积木派对游戏，支持<strong>2到4位玩家</strong>游玩！<br>操作简单易上手，可胜利之路并不平坦。<br>率先到达目的地，或是坚持到最后！<br><i>《Block'Em!》</i>融合了<strong>平台游戏和解谜游戏</strong>的相关元素，玩法更加有趣刺激。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>冲向终点，挺到最后！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776680/extras/testrace1.gif?t=1704818446\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用积木搭设道路，或是将它们消除！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776680/extras/Build_bridge_or_burn.gif?t=1704818446\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>将友谊大力推至岌岌可危的边缘！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776680/extras/on_the_brink.gif?t=1704818446\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与你的朋友（或者敌人）来一起畅玩，最多支持4名玩家线上或本地游玩！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776680/extras/play_with_enemies.gif?t=1704818446\" /></span>",
